snippet: Graeme McDowell rolled in two long putts early and kept bogeys off his card to hold the lead at the World Challenge in Thousand Oaks, Calif.
abstract: Graeme McDowell takes third-round lead at World Challenge golf tournament in Thousand Oaks, Calif.
